title: TomTom Navigator Maps v675.1409 for ALL DEVICES - UK and Ireland
description:
~~~~~~~~~~RAPIDSHARE MIRROR~~~~~~~~~~~

STEP ONE NOT APPLICABLE

1. Extract the rar file to your HD while maintaining the included folder structure.
2. Copy the complete folder to the root of your device Memory Card (you can exclude the exe file if you wish)
3. In case you don&#039;t have your TT device ID code, then start TT6 and select the map you have just copied.
4. The map will give you the device ID and will ask you to enter the map&#039;s registration code.
5. On your PC, double click the exe file included in the maps foder and enter your Device ID.
6. The crack file will give you 3 serials for the different systems, choose what you need and close. 

THESE MAPS WILL NOT REQUIRE ACTIVATION IF YOU ARE USING A CRACKED SYMBIAN NOKIA s60v3 TOMTOM APPLICATION

COMPATIBLE WITH Pocket PC / Palm / Symbian / TT One / TT Go
Will not work with Navigator 5 mobile software
